node.text:
Your comfort zone is just that...comfortable.

If you want to grow you have to put yourself in uncomfortable positions where you'll have opportunities to gain new skills and lose old habits.

Follow us @businessinstantly

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021 tagging @chitabnb. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb How I built a $2.4M Airbnb business without owning any properties. Story time. (A thread)'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb In late 2017 my sales company went bankrupt, lost all my money and had to start all over again.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb In December 2017 didn't have enough money to pay rent and hao had to move in with my parents and I put the property was renting at the time on Airbnb.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb A month went by I noticed the property listed on Airbnb actually made more money than I was paying for rent at the time. At that moment I realized could turn this into a real business.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb I spent all my time learning everything could about the Airbnb business and created a strategy that allowed me to fino properties that would make me at least $2K per month after all expenses.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb I started using credit to lease properties and listed them on Airbnb with the owner's permission. By March 2018 added 7 more properties, which combined were making me $20K per month in profit.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb I ended 2018 with 30 properties and scalee my business to $2.4M. In 2019 doubled my earnings and kept adding 1 property per month.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb During 2020 while countless people went out of business, my strategy allowed me to keep adding properties and growing my Airbnb business.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb This year my plan is to keep adding more properties and teach others how to start and grow an Airbnb business.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 10, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Chi Ta @itschitabnb This is the story of how I built my Airbnb business over the the last 3 years. If you'd like to see more content and tips about building an Airbnb business, drop me a follow.'.

Fail at the first couple and then find one thing to big on" -Kevin o 'Leary let-Worth: $400M BUSINESS INSTANTLY'.

node.text:
Your 20s are prime time to start building a generational empire. You're still young and have time to fail over and over again before finding what works for you.

This is exactly what I did. I started with dropshipping and transitioned into digital marketing by building instagram and other social media pages.

If you have the time take advantage of it!

Follow us @businessinstantly

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'WHERE IT ALL STARTED Apple Google Amazon ማυ..E Harley Disney Lamborghini BUSINESS INSTANTLY'.

node.text:
You don't need a lot to get started. A consistent work ethic and a good mindset will get you farther than a fancy work space.

Disney paid $10 a month for rent to produce videos in the back of a small office...no excuses.

Follow us @businessinstantly

node.text:
It's all about money management. The cash you have is all that matters. Savings and investments that are put away and making money consistently is what's important.

If you have very little in checking its important to keep stacking more cashflow so you can continue investing and watch the money compound.

Follow us @businessinstantly
